                        <interp inst="t18430918-name-83" type="surname" value="FARNBOROUGH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430918-name-83" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH FARNBOROUGH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a coal-dealer—the prisoner was in my em<lb></lb>ploy—he carried out coals, and should bring the money back for them—Mrs. Smith dealt with me—the prisoner did not pay me any money from her on or about the 17th of August—I discharged him on Saturday the 19th—I ascer<lb></lb>tained, on the 21st, that it had been paid—he went with me on Tuesday to Mrs. Smith, to clear up his case—he abused her, and afterwards admitted that he had received it, and offered me the 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. HORRY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> How long was he in your service? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Four months—he had 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. per week—I have found out a great deal since he left me.</p>
